《'''我爱上的人是奇葩'''》（{{lang-en|'''''You're the Worst'''''}}）是一部[[美国|美国]]喜劇电视剧，于2014年7月17日在[[FX_(电视频道)|FX]]首播的电视剧，第二季開始移至FXX播出。<ref name="cast">{{Cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/09/fx-rounds-out-cast-for-toxic-romance-comedy-youre-the-worst/|title=FX Rounds Out Cast For Toxic-Romance Comedy 'You're The Worst'|work=Deadline|date=September 19, 2013|accessdate=July 10, 2014|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714132046/http://www.deadline.com/2013/09/fx-rounds-out-cast-for-toxic-romance-comedy-youre-the-worst/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/listings/20140616fx05/|title=(#101) "Pilot"|work=The Futon Critic|accessdate=July 10, 2014}}</ref>影集講述自我中心的作家吉米({{link-en|克里斯·吉爾|Chris Geere}}飾演)與具有自我毀滅傾向的公關主管格蕾琴({{link-en|艾雅·凱許|Aya Cash}}飾演)嘗試發展一段感情，而他們的朋友埃德加({{link-en|德斯敏·伯吉斯|Desmin Borges}}飾演)與琳賽({{link-en|凱瑟·唐納休|Kether Donohue}}飾演)也參與其中<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.thestar.com/entertainment/television/2016/11/06/all-hail-the-rise-of-the-reasonably-competent-tv-heroine.html |title=All hail the rise of the reasonably competent TV heroine |work=Toronto Star |date=November 5, 2016 |first=Sophie |last=Van Bastelaer |accessdate=November 8, 2016 |archive-date=2016-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161109083752/https://www.thestar.com/entertainment/television/2016/11/06/all-hail-the-rise-of-the-reasonably-competent-tv-heroine.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="cast"/>。

影集於2014年7月17日首播<ref>{{Cite press|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2014/05/16/fx-and-fxx-set-summer-premiere-dates-for-original-series-639213/20140516fx01/|title=FX and FXX Set Summer Premiere Dates for Original Series|publisher=FX|date=May 16, 2014|accessdate=July 10, 2014}}</ref>。2014年9月30日，FX續訂了13集的第二季，並於2015年9月9日於FXX首播<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.zap2it.com/blogs/youre_the_worst_married_renewed-2014-09|title='You're the Worst' and 'Married' renewed for Season 2 by FX|last=Rackham|first=Casey|publisher=Zap2it|date=September 30, 2014|accessdate=October 1, 2014|archive-date=2015-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150708032754/http://www.zap2it.com/blogs/youre_the_worst_married_renewed-2014-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第二季-{聚焦}-於[[重度憂鬱症|重度憂鬱症]]以及其對現代感情生活的影響。2016年9月，FX續訂影集第四季<ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2016/tv/news/youre-the-worst-renewed-at-fxx-for-season-4-1201873035/ |title=‘You’re the Worst’ Renewed at FXX for Season 4 |work=Variety |last=Holloway |first=Daniel |date=September 28, 2016 |accessdate=September 28, 2016 |archive-date=2016-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160929140150/https://variety.com/2016/tv/news/youre-the-worst-renewed-at-fxx-for-season-4-1201873035/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> ，並於2017年9月6日首播<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvline.com/2017/06/28/youre-the-worst-season-4-premiere-date-better-things-season-2-fx/ |title=You're the Worst Season 4, Better Things Season 2 Get Premiere Dates |publisher=TVLine |last=Schwartz |first=Ryan |date=June 28, 2017 |accessdate=June 28, 2017 |archive-date=2017-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170628204841/http://tvline.com/2017/06/28/youre-the-worst-season-4-premiere-date-better-things-season-2-fx/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2017年11月，FX續訂影集最終第五季，並於2019年1月9日首播。劇終集於2019年4月3日播出。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2017/tv/news/youre-the-worst-renewed-season-5-last-season-fxx-1202615687/ |title=‘You’re the Worst’ Renewed for Fifth and Final Season at FXX |work=Variety |l